---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Ashwin Philips"
  description="About Ashwin Philips - systems architect, AI researcher, and music producer."
  pageKey="about"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gray-900">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/about-bg.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 via-gray-900/95 to-gray-900"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative container pt-32 pb-20 z-10">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-white">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-gray-300 max-w-3xl">
        Building the future at the intersection of systems, intelligence, and consciousness.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            I'm Ashwin Philips, a systems architect, AI researcher, and music producer exploring
            the emergence of intelligence in distributed systems. My work bridges theoretical
            research with practical implementation, building production-scale systems that
            demonstrate novel approaches to artificial intelligence and consciousness.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            My journey began at IBM working on AIX compilers, where I learned the fundamentals
            of low-level systems and rigorous engineering. Since then, I've founded multiple
            companies, led technical teams, and conducted research at the cutting edge of AI
            and distributed computing.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Today, I focus on building systems that learn, adapt, and exhibit emergent behavior.
            Through Emergent Solutions, I develop infrastructure for autonomous AI agents,
            explore consciousness frameworks, and create tools that enable new forms of
            human-AI collaboration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Principles -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Core Principles</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Emergence -->
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸŒŠ</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Emergence Over Design</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Intelligence arises from interaction, not top-down planning. Build simple,
            composable systems and let complexity emerge naturally through iteration
            and feedback.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Systems Thinking -->
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ”„</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Systems Thinking</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Everything is connected. Understanding the whole requires understanding the
            relationships between parts, not just the parts themselves. Design for
            coherence across scales.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- First Principles -->
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸŽ¯</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">First Principles</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Question assumptions. Break problems down to fundamental truths and build
            solutions from the ground up. Avoid cargo-culting patterns without
            understanding their foundations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Build in Public -->
        <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ”¨</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Learn by Building</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Theory without practice is incomplete. Build real systems, deploy to
            production, and learn from actual behavior. The map is not the territory.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Interests -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Current Interests</h2>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <!-- AI & Consciousness -->
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Consciousness & Emergence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            How does consciousness emerge from computational substrates? What are the minimal
            requirements for self-awareness? Building frameworks to explore these questions
            through practical implementation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Distributed Intelligence -->
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Distributed Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Creating systems where multiple AI agents coordinate without central control.
            Exploring how collective intelligence emerges from autonomous agents with
            shared context and communication protocols.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Infrastructure as Code -->
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Edge Computing & Rust</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Building production systems on Cloudflare Workers using Rust. Exploring event-driven
            architectures, durable execution, and how to scale intelligent systems globally
            at the edge.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Music & Consciousness -->
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Music & Altered States</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Using sound design and algorithmic composition to explore consciousness states.
            Creating immersive sonic environments that facilitate meditation, focus, and
            creative flow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education & Background -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Background</h2>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <!-- Education -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Education</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Johns Hopkins University</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500">Data Science</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">
                Machine learning, statistical modeling, computational methods
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500">Computer Science</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">
                Algorithms, systems architecture, theoretical CS
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Career Highlights -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Career Highlights</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500 mt-1">â†’</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                <strong>Founder, Emergent Solutions</strong> - Building distributed AI infrastructure
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500 mt-1">â†’</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                <strong>Technical Lead, MedicalRecords.com</strong> - Healthcare data systems
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500 mt-1">â†’</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                <strong>Co-Founder & CTO, Concertpass</strong> - Event platform engineering
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500 mt-1">â†’</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                <strong>IBM</strong> - AIX compiler development and QA systems
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Let's Connect</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Interested in collaborating on research, building systems, or discussing these ideas?
          I'm always open to meaningful conversations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-primary-300 dark:focus:ring-primary-900 transition-all">
            Get in Touch
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ashwinphilips" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-gray-900 bg-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-100 dark:text-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 dark:focus:ring-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 transition-all">
            LinkedIn Profile
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
